<section class="mt-32">
  <h2 class="font-extrabold text-5xl tracking-tight">Things people actually ask us</h2>

  <div class="mt-12">
    <p class="font-medium text-xl text-gray-900 mt-4">What is Relay?</p>
    <p class="mt-2 leading-5 text-gray-600">
      <span class="block mb-2">Relay is Zimbabwe's long-distance ride-sharing platform.</span>
      <span class="block mb-2">We connect drivers who have empty seats with passengers travelling the same route.</span>
      <span class="block mb-2">Instead of empty cars or unpredictable hitchhiking, drivers and passengers can plan their journeys in advance, hours or days before departure.</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-8">
    <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">For drivers</h2>

    <details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">Do I need to change my plans?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>No. You only list trips you're already taking, Relay just helps you fill empty seats and save on fuel and tollgate costs.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">How do payments work?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>Passengers place a small commitment to secure their seat. This helps avoid no-shows, and you receive the agreed amount for the trip. You also pay a small commitment fee for the trip.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">How does the driver commitment fee work?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>When a passenger requests your ride, you pay a once-off $1 to unlock their details and accept or decline. If more passengers request the same trip, those are free.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">What if no one books my ride?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>Nothing changes. You still take your trip as planned, there's no risk in listing.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl mt-12 mb-4">For passengers</h2>

    <details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">How do I find a ride?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>Search your route, choose a driver, and request a seat. It takes less than a minute.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">Why is there a commitment payment?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>A small commitment of 50 cents secures your seat and shows the driver you're serious. It helps reduce cancellations and keeps rides reliable.</p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="group border-t border-b border-gray-200 py-6">
      <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
        <span class="block">Can I trust the driver?</span>
        <%= inline_svg_tag "caret.svg", class: "block transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180" %>
      </summary>
      <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600">
        <p>You can view driver details, car info and after booking, and you can still decide to cancel if you don't feel safe or if something feels off to you.</p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>
</section>
